Web Application Incident Report – DoS Attack Analysis

1. Introduction

This report provides a detailed analysis of a Denial of Service (DoS) attack detected in the web server logs. The purpose of this report is to identify the source of the attack, analyze its behavior, determine the targeted resources, and propose effective mitigation strategies to prevent similar incidents in the future.

